msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho ahaṃ, bhante, nigaṇṭhaṃ nāṭaputtaṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr "and asked him the same question."

msgctxt "dn2:40.5"
msgid "‘yathā nu kho imāni, bho aggivessana, puthusippāyatanāni …"
