msgctxt "dn2:40.6"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:40.7"
msgid ""
"sakkā nu kho, bho aggivessana, evameva diṭṭheva dhamme sandiṭṭhikaṃ "
"sāmaññaphalaṃ paññapetun’ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a>
#. VAR: nigaṇṭho → nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "dn2:41.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhante, nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "He said:"

msgctxt "dn2:41.2"
msgid "‘idha, mahārāja, nigaṇṭho cātuyāmasaṃvarasaṃvuto hoti."
msgstr ""
"‘Great king, consider a Jain ascetic who is restrained in the fourfold "
"restraint."

msgctxt "dn2:41.3"
msgid "Kathañca, mahārāja, nigaṇṭho cātuyāmasaṃvarasaṃvuto hoti?"
msgstr "And how is a Jain ascetic restrained in the fourfold restraint?"

msgctxt "dn2:41.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, mahārāja, nigaṇṭho sabbavārivārito ca hoti, sabbavāriyutto ca, "
"sabbavāridhuto ca, sabbavāriphuṭo ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a Jain ascetic is obstructed by all water, devoted to all water, "
"shaking off all water, pervaded by all water."

msgctxt "dn2:41.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, mahārāja, nigaṇṭho cātuyāmasaṃvarasaṃvuto hoti."
msgstr "That’s how a Jain ascetic is restrained in the fourfold restraint."

msgctxt "dn2:41.6"
msgid "Yato kho, mahārāja, nigaṇṭho evaṃ cātuyāmasaṃvarasaṃvuto hoti;"
msgstr "When a Jain ascetic is restrained in the fourfold restraint,"

msgctxt "dn2:41.7"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, mahārāja, nigaṇṭho gatatto ca yatatto ca ṭhitatto cā’ti."
msgstr ""
"they’re called a knotless one who is self-realized, self-controlled, and "
"steadfast.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="32"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.58"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:42.1"
msgid ""
"Itthaṃ kho me, bhante, nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ puṭṭho "
"samāno cātuyāmasaṃvaraṃ byākāsi."
msgstr ""
"And so, when I asked Nigaṇṭha Nāṭaputta about the fruits of the ascetic life "
"apparent in the present life, he answered with the fourfold restraint."

