"breadfruit, or when asked about a breadfruit, answered with a mango."

msgctxt "dn2:42.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho me, bhante, nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ puṭṭho "
"samāno cātuyāmasaṃvaraṃ byākāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:42.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, etadahosi:"
