msgctxt "dn2:42.5"
msgid ""
"‘kathañhi nāma mādiso samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā vijite vasantaṃ apasādetabbaṃ "
"maññeyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘How could one such as I presume to rebuke an ascetic or brahmin living in "
"my realm?’"

msgctxt "dn2:42.6"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, bhante, nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandiṃ "
"nappaṭikkosiṃ."
msgstr ""
"So I neither approved nor dismissed that statement of Nigaṇṭha Nāṭaputta."

msgctxt "dn2:42.7"
msgid ""
"Anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā anattamano anattamanavācaṃ anicchāretvā tameva "
"vācaṃ anuggaṇhanto anikkujjanto uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamiṃ."
msgstr ""
"I was displeased, but did not express my displeasure. Neither accepting what "
"he said nor contradicting it, I got up from my seat and left."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn2:43.1"
msgid "3.6. Sañcayabelaṭṭhaputtavāda"
msgstr "The Doctrine of Sañjaya Belaṭṭhiputta"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:44.1"
msgid "Ekamidāhaṃ, bhante, samayaṃ yena sañcayo belaṭṭhaputto tenupasaṅkamiṃ;"
