msgstr ""
"Yet he amuses himself, supplied and provided with the five kinds of sensual "
"stimulation as if he was a god."

msgctxt "dn2:55.10"
msgid "Ahaṃ panamhissa kassako gahapatiko karakārako rāsivaḍḍhako."
msgstr ""
"Whereas I’m a farmer, a householder, a hard worker, someone who builds up "
"their capital."

msgctxt "dn2:55.11"
msgid "So vatassāhaṃ puññāni kareyyaṃ."
msgstr "I should do good deeds."

